DocPropertyConstant.Name: TBMSLURRYPRESSUREFACESUPPORT
DocPropertyConstant.Documentation: A closed-face shield designed for tunnelling in very soft, wet, or running ground by use of circulating, pressurized clay slurry against the face to counterbalance earth pressures exerted against the cutterhead, prevent ingress of water and also to carry away the excavated material; which moves forward by reacting against an installed lining.
